### The Science
**Logan** is built on research specifically centered on female physiology, which has historically been ignored in standard medical and athletic studies. By analyzing your **hormonal stage** alongside symptoms like your **deep fatigue** and **irregular cycles**, the system identifies patterns that general health apps miss. This allows for precise adjustments in nutrition and training that account for the unique way **estrogen** and **progesterone** affect your metabolism and recovery.

### The Real Talk
Think of me as the person who actually understands why you''re suddenly crying over a commercial or why your knees ache for no reason. Most apps treat everyone like they have the same steady hormones, but we know perimenopause is a wild ride that requires a different map. You don''t have to figure this out alone or wonder if you''re just "getting old"—you''re just transitioning, and having the right data makes that feel a lot less scary.'
